"A Makefile and a Windows command file can be generated for you so that you\n"
"only have to run e.g. `make html' instead of invoking sphinx-build\n"
"directly."
msgstr "Makefile dan berkas perintah Windows dapat dibuatkan untuk Anda sehingga Anda\ncukup menjalankan misalnya `make html' alih-alih memanggil sphinx-build\nsecara langsung."

#: cmd/quickstart.py:416
msgid "Create Makefile? (y/n)"
msgstr "Buat Makefile? (y/n)"

#: cmd/quickstart.py:420
msgid "Create Windows command file? (y/n)"
msgstr "Buat berkas perintah Windows? (y/n)"

#: cmd/quickstart.py:472 ext/apidoc/_generate.py:76
#, python-format
